    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my reliable daily driver, and it's looking for a brand new home! This car has been so good to me\u2014it's in solid shape and runs like a dream. It's been well-loved and carefully maintained, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for a dependable ride that still feels fresh. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
